OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome patchy
OL,6,Flow cloud will cover many of the hills
OL,7,Fto the north. Isolated showers and
OL,8,Fpotential thunderstorms in the east to
OL,9,Fstart. Turning to light rain by
OL,10,Fmorning. A cooler night for some but
OL,11,Fstaying quite muggy.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FA cloudy start for many but
OL,14,Fwill lift and break through the day.
OL,15,FStaying hot and dry but temperatures
OL,16,Fslightly down on recent days.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
